        "faqs": {
          "title": "Frequently Asked Questions",
          "subtitle": "Everything you need to know about Dockly",
          "items": [
            {
              "question": "What is Dockly and how does it work?",
              "answer": "Dockly is an all-in-one workspace that brings together everything across your digital life in one beautiful, intelligent interface."
            },
            {
              "question": "Is my data secure and private?",
              "answer": "Absolutely. We use enterprise-grade encryption, secure cloud infrastructure, and never share your personal data with third parties."
            },
            {
              "question": "Can I try Dockly for free?",
              "answer": "Yes! We offer waitlist subscribers 1-month free with full access to all features. No credit card required."
            },
            {
              "question": "How does Dockly integrate with my existing tools?",
              "answer": "Dockly is intended to be a Hub that connects all your essential accounts, services, files, and tools.  Dockly seamlessly connects with popular tools like Google Calendar and Drive, Microsoft Outlook, DropBox, Financial Institutions and Health tracking applications. "
            },
            {
              "question": "What support options are available?",
              "answer": "We currenlty provide 24/7 email support and will be rolling out community support channels along with live chat during business hours."
            },
            {
              "question": "Can I use Dockly on mobile devices?",
              "answer": "Yes - Dockly is available through Mobile Web currently, accessible through your favorite browser with iOS and Android apps in the works.  We are proudly a Web First application as we believe your life is best managed on the big screen.  "
            }
          ]
        },
